SELECT i.product_id, p.name, i.quantity, w.location FROM Inventory i JOIN Product p ON i.product_id = p.product_id JOIN Warehouse w ON i.warehouse_id = w.warehouse_id WHERE i.quantity > 50 ORDER BY w.location DESC, i.quantity DESC;

SELECT s.shipment_id, p.name AS product_name, s.quantity, s.destination FROM Shipment s JOIN Product p ON s.product_id = p.product_id WHERE s.quantity BETWEEN 100 AND 200 ORDER BY p.name ASC, s.quantity DESC LIMIT 5;
